    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<ol>\n<li>File tab -&gt; Invalidate Caches/Restart (then choose invalidate and restart from the dialog that will appear)</li>\n<li>Build tab -&gt; Clean Project</li>\n<li>Build tab -&gt; Rebuild Project</li>\n</ol>\n<p>This solution is just the same as @Ehsan_Haghdoust solution but letting Android Studio do that for me instead of doing that my self.</p>\n"
